Which is no problem for me because I'd
attended every class, so I'm totally prepared.

54
00:05:03,680 --> 00:05:09,277
<i>Then I see myself running down the hall</i>
<i>at school. This is very interesting, I think. </i>

55
00:05:09,440 --> 00:05:13,752
<i>It's not really my school. </i>
<i>It's the school from the next district. </i>

56
00:05:13,920 --> 00:05:16,434
- Go on!
- Even though I arrive early,

57
00:05:16,600 --> 00:05:20,593
<i>everybody is already there,</i>
<i>but the surprising part is... </i>

58
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:25,036
<i>I'm the only one who's prepared. </i>

59
00:05:26,880 --> 00:05:29,872
- You'll have to get out.
- You can't do this.

60
00:05:30,040 --> 00:05:31,917
Sure I can, Lionel.

61
