01:24:48,280 --> 01:24:50,271
<i># Take away my inhibition</i>

1003
01:24:52,120 --> 01:24:54,350
<i># Take away my solitude</i>

1004
01:24:56,040 --> 01:24:58,031
<i># Fire me up with your resistance</i>

1005
01:24:58,200 --> 01:25:00,395
<i># Mmm, put me in the mood</i>

1006
01:25:03,880 --> 01:25:06,269
<i># Stone the walls around this prison</i>

